# ğŸ“‰ Time Series Experiment No. 1: The Phase Shock

## ğŸ¯ Experiment Objective
To investigate the impact of a sudden **Phase Shift (180Â° / $\pi$ radians)** on a stable periodic signal. This simulates a "system reset" or "timing error" in a continuous process (e.g., a skipped heartbeat or a sensor desynchronization).

